---
import StaticArticlePage from '@/components/ui/StaticArticlePage.astro'
---

<StaticArticlePage
  description="Privacy policy for SeniorPath."
  kicker="Legal"
  title="Privacy Policy"
>
  <h2>Local storage</h2>
  <p>
    SeniorPath stores small pieces of information in your browser to preserve theme preference and guide completion
    state. This helps keep the experience consistent between visits on the same device.
  </p>

  <h2>Analytics and tracking</h2>
  <p>
    SeniorPath may use Cloudflare Web Analytics for lightweight site-level traffic measurement, such as pageviews,
    top pages, and referrers. This is intended for aggregate website analytics rather than behavioral profiling or
    ad targeting.
  </p>
  <p>
    Local browser storage used by SeniorPath is limited to theme preference, locale preference, and guide
    completion state. Analytics configuration and data handling by Cloudflare are governed by Cloudflare's own
    service and privacy terms.
  </p>

  <h2>Third-party services</h2>
  <p>
    Links to external services or reference material may be governed by separate privacy terms and policies.
  </p>

  <h2>Updates</h2>
  <p>
    This policy may be revised as the product changes. Material updates should be reflected on this page.
  </p>
</StaticArticlePage>
